content.detailedDescription:
This photograph was taken using a cellular camera saturday in stafford virginia on 25 feb 17 around 935pm behind my house. i noticed a bright whiter light object hovering above the school parking lot lightd possibly further behind the parking lot over scattered homes and a wooded area lot.  the object appeared about 1,250 yard's away.  i stood on the deck and took the picture, the light was silent and made no sound, it was there longer than 40 minutes, i thought maybe it was a helicopter or plane coming toward me, giving the illusion of a stationary light, but it just stayed hovering for a long time, no change is size or dimension. however, when you enlarge the photo you can see a bright v shape uncharacteristic of a airplane or helicopter? only other thing it could of been is a stealth fighter with that v shape, but the v is the entire frontal length of the aircraft a stealth doesn't have a long v like that. if you enlarge th we picture the v appears to be the propulsion system with a saturn like ring around the objects middle with a do like top. and what appears to be an energy field or forcefield around the craft,possibly a potential cloaking device.

after careful review of the photograph i am convinced what i witnessed that night was either a us government project and that's ok, or a true alien space craft.

you can see a day photograph taken in the same place as the ufo photograph the night prior and can early see the parking lots lights of the school in relation to the ufo.

my wife also witnessed that object with me and she thinks she may have seen it again later that night but it slightly moved to the right.
content.summary: Bright lights glowing white star like about 200feet to 500 feet above treeline.

content.detailedDescription: On friday 24th did anyone else see a bright silver balloon about 1135 ?. i was waiting for a dellivery at work and was watching overflights with my binoculars , a b787 nor , had just gone towards gatwick and two westbound trails were almost overhead , has i focused on the larger aircraft , a b747 prob lufthansa i saw a bright flash near to the jet , i was able to steady the binoculars against the door frame of the workshop , i saw a small black sphere or orb with a brilliant silver crescent like a new moom on the sunward side . the object was lost for a few min while i looked at the airliners but was in the same place when i looked back at the same place , i was able to get a clear sharp focus on the silver crecent but one of the many clouds coverd the object and i did not see it again when the clouds had passed . i have seen several orange weather balloons but never one like this despite the high windspeed on friday the object appeared to be rock steady in position . my workmate could not see the object with the naked eye . poss some sort of unmaned uav observation system ?
content.summary: A stationary black orb with brilliant silver crescent seen .

content.detailedDescription: Not sure the objects i've seen are ufos, but since 2/23 there has been something unusual in the sky. thurs 2/23 heard alot of planes flying in the afternoon, continued in evening. heavy sounding like cargo. took binoculars out to view these planes around 8:20 pm. noticed bright star low in the distance, became jellyfish like with binoculars. it pulsated as it seemed to hover a few minutes and then seemed to descend slowly below the trees. went out next night at 8:40 pm. it was there in the west again, but further away and lower. sky was cloud covered on 2/25 and did not see the bright star. last night at 8:10 pm. again it was in the sky, but this time i looked at the stars high in the sky and viewed one to the south hovering high. while i watched the object to the west, something moved fast through lower section of binoculars. adjusted vision and saw the same type of object moving north, rather low in the sky. i have heard nothing on our local news. keep hearing a lot of plane traffic. seems to be a schedule for these objects. i'm going to keep watching to see how long this goes on. may not be ufos, but not normal.
content.summary: After hearing planes went outside with binoculars, spotted bright starlike image low in the west. object looked like transparent jellyfish with pulsating colors, nothing solid to view

i have attached a photo

content.detailedDescription:
Goose creek sc has strange v shaped crafts hovering above the city.  there is a you tube posting for this area, looks like what i am seeing.  you can see a string of lights that make up the v. one of the crafts seemed to have a little craft floating near by at all times.  is this survalence? we have a new police station recently built, city patrol with new technology? weirdest thing to see these brighter than a star objects in the sky.  we also have a naval weapons station here, are we being watched? what gives.  sure would like to know what is messing up my view of the stars everynight.  
have contacted you once before about a craft my friend and i witnessed in garden city a few years ago.  this could very well be the same craft we saw then.  it was parked in the air above a radio tower next to the king fisher inn.  we were on the penthouse roof top area when we observed this craft.  after some debate with my friend as to what it was, that craft came down parked in front of our balcony and gave us a look as if intentional, like it heard our conversation.  wow true story! it took off over the water toward myrtle beach and was gone in a blink of an eye, never made a sound or disturbed any air around it!  
we went back the next year and the radio tower that had been there forever was moved...A parking lot is there now.  but i never took my eyes off the sky again, and now...What is in my backyard sky? they were all over us last night. they sit lower than airplanes fly or just above the flight path or pattern.  i'm not the only one seeing these strange lights parked in the sky but i can't figure out why no one is talking about them.  must be ours to be so obvious i figure...But why are they there.  big brother? what gives i wonder. we are watching them right back!
content.summary: These crafts have been in the sky for a while, last night saw more than ever

content.detailedDescription:
Date:  26 feb 2017

time:  4:08 am

location:  gettysburg.  front porch of house having a smoke.

direction of flight:  sw

speed: would guess somewhere in the range of 800 mph and up.  traveling very low but not so fast you couldn't keep track of it.

shape:  straight line w/ a slight curve.  was still dark so i couldn't get a good look at it.

brightness:  very very bright maybe as bright or brighter than one of those million watt candle power flashlights.

length:  if you would of held up a yard stick to it. it probably would have covered it.  to me it appeared to be between 800 to 1000 feet long.

maneuvering:  i seen this bright line of lights coming from the se heading directly over gettysburg at least 800 to 1000 feet up.   i thought it was a jet or plane so kept watching it because of how very low it was and all these lights in a row.  it then turned slightly heading my direction which was northerly but just a few seconds in its turn, it turned right back toward a sw direction toward fairfield with no difficulties whatsoever, for the size of the craft.

sound:  a very low humming sound.  at first i thought it could have been a large jet, but at that close of a distance and height, the engines would have been roaring and most definitely you would have been able to identify it as being a jet.

appearance:  all i can say it was a basic line with a slight curve with at least 10 to 12 lights,  all bright bright white.  no red, no blue, and none blinking.


age:  59
retired federal employee
army veteran
content.summary: Observed line of bright lights moving from se to sw direction over gettysburg

content.detailedDescription: We were watching tv in our hotel room on the beach and noticed what we thought was an extremely bright star in the sky above the ocean. when we went out on the balcony for a closer look, we noticed it had something attached to it underneath. it seemed be coming toward our direction but was still in the same location in the sky. it remained there for at least an hour. it i ran to get my camera to try to zoom in and take a picture and get a better look of what it was, but then had to walk my dogs for the night. when i came back it was gone.

content.detailedDescription: I was laying in bed at about midnight and couldn't sleep, so i looked out the windows along the wall of my bedroom as i often do when i cant fall asleep. i was watching the stars, when i noticed one of them acting unnaturally. it was hovering above one of the nearby hills and at first i thought it was an airplane or a satellite. as i watched it, it proceeded to get dimmer and brighter, slowly flashing continuously. the coloring was different than that of a star; it wasn't white light but rather a reddish orange with a surrounding pinkish orange aura. it remained mostly stationary except for a slight bobbing motion as it moved up and down where it was and seemed to be rotating as it brightened and dimmed. it moved side to side a few times as well, but still hovered relatively in the same spot. as i watched it, it eventually started blinking a smaller red light and yellow light rhythmically as it appeared to rotate. i looked nearby along the hills to see if there was anything else unusual, and saw three white "stars" remaining stationary low along the tops of the hills as well. one was brighter than the two others but that was all i observed. i returned my attention to the main one that was flashing. when i stared at it continuously, everything except it would darken and get dimmer as it rotated, and i felt glued to watching it. i otherwise felt normal. i continued to watch it for probably approximately half an hour before passing out. i do not remember falling asleep.
content.summary: Watching from bedroom window around midnight, saw flashing starlike object hovering over hilltops and emitting colored light

content.detailedDescription: The night sky is clear tonight and i was outside briefly when i noticed a small pinpoint size starlike object moving diagonally from about 50 degrees up from the horizon in the south. it was moving seemingly faster than a satellite on a steep angle toward the southwest. at first it moved in a straight line downward and then it started to zigzag slightly - straight west then down - several times.  that in itself changed my mind about it potentially being a satellite.  then it grew to about 10x it's size and brightened for about 10 seconds and then regressed to its original pinpoint size and at about 20 degrees above the horizon it disappeared.
content.summary: At 7:24 pm in a clear night sky, i saw a slow moving pinpoint starlike object moving diagonally downward from south to sw for about 30 degrees.  it brightened and grew in size and then reduced to a pinpoint and disappeared at about 20degrees above horizon

content.detailedDescription:
For us, beginning on january 22 and reoccurring frequently through february 23rd, a large illuminated 3d donut like sphere with a dark center; and sometimes two identical looking spheres but never more than two, began appearing due east of our home towards wimberely, texas which is 9 miles away. the first sighting occurred as i went to the back door (north side of the house), to make sure it was locked for the night at 10:00 pm, and thought i saw to the east what i usually see over the trees at a reasonably low altitude - a star, but this made me pause and look again because it emitted red and green pulses of light through a golden and white light signature. then it moved around, so i quickly called my wife to look at it also. it hovered and bop around for five to ten minutes, and then in my estimate slowly move in an arc path towards the se along ranch road 12 towards san marcos, texas which is approximately 35 miles away. once they begin to move away, and never at the same exact time, it is always slowly but at a constant rate of speed. my guess would be approximately 60 mph+.

the objects, when there are two of them, are identical in shape, size, coloration, motion, and behavior in the same directional view from our back porch. we see them appear out of nothing, and we see them after they have appeared above the trees at about 15-20 degrees above the horizon. they spin in two directions simultaneously (a wheel within a wheel,) as they jump and bop around within a reasonably confined area within our view. they go up and down but never in extreme ranges and do not land while we observe them. they pulse (emit) or flicker a few green (short and narrow) beams, longer red beams or rays of light, and they emit a wider beam of golden light in a 360 degree 3d pattern within a general white aura of light around the object. there are also harder to see black bicycle spoked lines around the outer edge of the sphere. my wife couldn't see the green light, but agrees with me on the other three dominate colors. pulsing is the best word to describe the light emissions, but to me the short green rays and slightly longer red beams stick out like steady fixed thorns or quills.

as of february 23rd my wife has seen them seven times and i have seen them six times in the same area between 8:00 pm and 10:00 pm cst, with one exception. at 01:00 in mid february my wife saw one south west of the house with no information given as to height or distance or subsequent activity - she went back to bed.

our response was one of interest and wonder to finally see with our own eyes what others have talked about our whole lives. this is our first sighting of anything unusual. my impression is that they are preprogrammed scouts or probes collecting data, but where they are appearing is only cattle country full of limestone rock with a few scattered homes. please note that we are moving away from this property within the next week to a location overseas, so our phone numbers will not be working then, but our emails should be working. we have planned this move for a year, so this was a nice gift of last minute luck for us. thank you for your great work in this area. the attached video was done with an apple phone. i hope you can enhance it to meet your needs.
content.summary: Sphere emitting multicolors hovered near wimberley and proceeded towards san marcos tx during a month long visitation so far.

content.detailedDescription:
I was on my computer all day. then i went outside to check and see what was above my room. at first it looked like a glowing boomerang shape or parachute with no person attached.

so i went back to the room to grab the camera, it only took 1 minute from the original sighting for it to change direction and ascend without me seeing it. when i got back out to backyard to film it, it had already ascended to approximately 10,000 ft above ground. watched it for a few minutes. 

at the time when i was filming the object it was an orb like. and followed it to my neighbor's front lawn and it was already too far away to the east.

at 6 pm i was already back in my computer and heard 3 sonic booms. the next afternoon at 5 pm, after work i saw 3 f-16s taking off from mcas miramar heading north to go back to their home base.

at the airshow i asked where the f-16s were coming from, the marine told me that it was mcas yuma that called for f-16s to intercept this ufo. so they came back to miramar only to file report, refuel and rest before heading home.
content.summary: Object was above my house at about 1000 ft when i first sighted it. sonic booms were heard after 6 pm.

content.detailedDescription:
At the time i was about 12 and spending the night at my best friends house. her bedroom overlooked backyard which had wooded area behind it. we both woke up to a loud buzzing type sound and looked out her bedroom window to see an object hovering just over the trees approximately 200' away. it was as large as the house, dark silver colored  and had round port-like windows all around the edge of it; resembling a typical spacecraft that you'd always see portrayed. we were scared but mesmerized by the lights omitted from its windows in a quick rotation around the circumference of object.
it hovered for what seemed like  several minutes and then very rapidly shot away until we no longer could view from bedroom window. this happened in mid-late 1960's and i recall the event as vividly today as i did 50 years ago. i didn't know this mufon site existed until my best friend told me about it a few days ago.
content.summary: Object roughly size of house hovered above trees in back of yard, with light pulsing and flashing out its round windows

content.detailedDescription:
Nací en 1979 en junio, desde que tenía 4 años de edad hasta mis 12 años aproximadamente he tenido pesadillas que eran recurrentes donde me lavnataba a media noche lllrnsdo desesperado y aterrado y mis padres tardaban horas en hacer que recuperará la calma, en mis pesadillas los actores cambiaban su forma según cada pesadilla, unas veces se les veía otras veces no, a veces con forma de robots, otras de monstruos. siempre me veía en una habitación sumamente oscura y frente a mí una gran pantalla luminosa como las pantallas led que hoy son comunes pero que en aquella época eran solo ficción, en esa pantalla aparecían varias secuencias de números que yo debía seguir o completar con mi mano sobre aquella pantalla presionando números aleatorios, esas entidades me obligaban a hacer esa secuencia solo que nunca hablaban pero yo sabía lo quqe querían, luego esa secuencia se hacía más y más rápida y cuando no podía seguir la secuencia ellos presionaban en mi mente para seguir haciéndolo y era cuando despertaba llorando y aterrorizado

estás pesadillas pasaban más o menos cada mes o a veces duraban tres o cuatro meses sin suceder y dejaron de pasar más o menos desde que cumplí 12 años,lo curioso es un niño de 4 años o hasta 6 y 7 con pesadillas de números que eran parecidos a lo que se conoce como la secuencia fibonacci que cuando la descubríamos después  la asocie de inm disto con mis pesadillas.

otro dato curioso es que cuando tenía 24 años sufrí unas convulsiones por un problema familiar que me llevó a esa situación y el hecho que me desmayara me llevaron a hacer unos estudios médicos entre ellos un electro encefalograma y radiografías de mi cerebro y el doctor juan josé sánchez encontró justo en el centro de mi cerebro un extraño cuerpo del tamaño de un grano de arroz que era anómalo y extraño lo que el describió como un tumor, me pidió que justo un año después volviera hacer los estudios para ver si cambiaba de tamaño y al hacerlo no había cambiado su tamaño original por lo que el doctor dijo que no me preocupara por el

siempre he tenido la curiosidad por el tema ovni, una vez a mis trece años junto a mi mamá y una amiga de la casa vimos a lo lejos a las 5:30 ok un ovni en forma de cigarro que subía lentamente en el cielo a lo lejos y luego como si hubiese volteado o girado de vertical a horizontal se convirtió en un punto que desapareció, siempre he investigado el tema ufo ovni, y a veces siento que no encajo en la sociedad, tengo algunas premoniciones que se cumplen y con mi esposa actualmente hemos tenido experiencias extrasensoriales en unas tres ocasiones en 5 años de casados,en las que cosas que pienso ella las ha recibido.

quisiera saber si esa experiencia q la cual nadie nunca me ha dado respuesta tenga algo que ver con el fenómeno ovni y sea producto de algún tipo de abducción ... muchas gracias amigos de mugon. espero pueda ayudarlos a en su busuqueda de la verdad...
content.summary: Desde que tengo 4 años de edad hasta los 12 años extraños sueños con seres roboticos que me colocan delante de pantalla de luz con secuencia de números me levantaban con pesadillas que me afectaban mucho

content.detailedDescription: Estava na varanda de casa observando a floresta(serra da cantareira), quando observei uma luz vermelha girando em alta velocidade, pensei ser um giro-flex de viatura policial, mas logo em seguida, começaram acender luzes amarelas, azuis e verdes.O objeto estava parado no solo,tinha aproximadamente 5 metros de diâmetro,e não dava para ver o seu formato real, apenas as luzes girando sequencialmente atrás de um bambuzal.Não emitia nenhum som e nenhuma fumaça.Espantado, chamei minha esposa que estava deitada no quarto, mas quando pronunciei seu nome, o objeto simplesmente apagou as luzes imediatamente e desapareceu!,sem emitir nenhum tipo de som ou rastro de fumaça.A partir deste evento, tento buscar explicação para o fato ocorrido.Aproximadamente um ano antes do ocorrido, observei quase que diariamente(durante 1 semana aproximadamente), uma luz branca pequena(do tamanho de uma bola de futebol), intensa e de brilho constante ficava  dentro do bambuzal,que por acaso ou não, antecedeu o nascimento da minha primeira filha.Um ano antes do nascimento da minha segunda filha esta mesma luz,só que em tamanho menor(bola de golf), entrou pela fresta da porta exatamente no momento em que eu e minha esposa estávamos tendo relação sexual.A luz entrou, parou em cima de mim e saiu em alta velocidade pela fresta da porta.A partir destes eventos, passei a observar(esporadicamente) luzes no céu.
content.summary: Em forma de disco, aprox. 05 metros de diâmetro, com luzes girando em velocidade média

content.detailedDescription:
Walking home around 2am from a friends house, i saw what looked like a shuttle from star trek. it was larger than a car, white on top and bottom with a row of lights on it's middle. it was moving without sound over the roof tops of buildings and as it traced the roofs, it shone a intense blue beam which i took to be measuring or xraying flats below.
a couple where walking up the other side of the street going in the opposite direction from me. as i shouted and waved for the attention of the craft, the couple saw it too. at that time, the object shone a light on me and moved over head. i am not sure exactly what happened but i found myself standing further back from where i was and the couple had gone. i continued with my walk home and found that a walk which usually took twenty minutes had taken forty.
the following morning was sunday and one of the glasgow news papers, (the sunday post,) had a story of an ufo being seen in clarkston which is a suburb on the south of glasgow. the description was the same as i had seen but my location was in the colston area on the north end of the city.
a week or so passed and while walking down the same road, the two other people saw me and came running to ask me what had happened that night. they said that the last time they saw me, i was taken in a beam of white light.
although i am not sure what happened exactly, i have a memory of meeting human people who told me that they where clones which had been produced to withstand  the extremes of space travel. it was then that a door at the front opened and the gray who was in charge came out. i'm don't know if that is a true memory or one which was implanted. i have heard other people say that they where abducted on t.V. and they told a similar story. i still have no clue what really happened that night and i don't know how to unravel the truth.
content.summary: I saw it move over a building and project a blue light which seemed to be xraying the occupents. i shouted and waved my arms to get it's attention. two other people saw it come over me and they said that i disapeard in a white light.

content.detailedDescription: My husband and i were outside at 8:45 pm watching a lightning storm off in the north sky and talking about our day when i noticed a bright light off to my left. at first i thought is was a falling star and immediately pointed the object out to my husband since he had his back towards it. the object was bright silver and shaped like a bullet or a cigar flying horizontal with the ground. a bright silver light trail was behind it and seemed to be headed toward the lighting storm.  right after i pointed it out to my husband it seemed to slow down and its brightness dimmed for a second or two then became bright again as it speed up and fly strait towards the lightning then just vanished.  i was excited that my husband was able to see the object and he is the one that urged my to come report it.
content.summary: Me & my husband were outside watching a lightning storm in the north sky when i noticed a bright object off to my left heading straight toward the lightning. at one piont it seamed to slow down and dim then became brighter as it got faster.

content.detailedDescription: I was letting my dog out to pee when my mother pointed out the ufo. i turned around and saw a very bright orb. at first, i thought it could have been an airplane, but the object was flying extremely fast- probably triple the amount of speed an airplane usually goes. it was also much brighter and flying much lower than an airplane. i could hear and feel a very low buzz as it passed. after this occurred and i could no longer see it, i felt very unnerved. i was confused for a good two minutes, as was my mother. i lost sight of it as it flew away and i was no longer able to see the object.
content.summary: It was a very bright orb that was going way too fast and was way too low to be an airplane.

content.detailedDescription:
My family was camping on an island in lake kabetogema, in northern minnesota. there was a severe thunder storm with lightning strikes very close and frequent. i called for help using a walkie talkie. reached a human service person (forest service?) who could provide no assistance due to the storm severity, remoteness of the site, and late night hour. i think lightening hit our tent. i had burned hair near the base of my neck. sometime during the night 4-5 small bluish somewhat apparition-like beings entered the tent. they did "rectal probes" on me and my family (4 people total). they explained this was a medical exam. i'm not sure where the dog was at this time. 

four trees were cut down and places around the perimeter of the tent. a 6 foot ? approximately-burn/bake circle was left on the ground with a fresh, crisp looking edge.  (different than a fire ring). the tree cuts were very smooth, no saw dust. 

sometime that morning i saw a large (8-10 feet tall) pink colored apparition-like man, no clothes but no body details visible. i recall this presence was reassuring and comforting.

some other encounters followed for a year or so. beings visited and talked to me in our family home. i once was pulled into the air from our deck. my parents grabbed me and i grabbed a tree. it felt like something was "sucking" me into the air. i heard someone say i would be dropped from a great height and crushed on a tree. previous to this i had communicated to hostile-feeling beings that they could land on a cloud, they may have died attempting to do this. it seemed like a revenge type of threat was happening. my impression was that these were different entities, reptile like people, large, male. 3-4 appeared in the house where i gave them a tour and they ate some food and beer. they disappeared suddenly. one appeared sick, with scales peeling or "fluffed" out. he seemed to recover a bit from eating tang drink mix. i kept one skin "scale" from these beings but this was removed from the house by men in black suits. i seemed to have further "telepathic" type communication with some beings for a time. they could appear and leave instantly.
content.summary: I was in 4th grade. our family was camping. there was a severe thunder storm. i called for help with a walkie talkie. saw 4-5 bluish small "people" with large black eyes. they seemed to provide medical exam and cut down 4 trees. left circle burn on ground
